# Target modern browsers only to reduce bundle size
# This excludes legacy browsers that need polyfills

# Production browsers
last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions

# Mobile browsers
last 2 iOS versions
last 2 ChromeAndroid versions

# Exclude old browsers
not IE 11
not dead
not op_mini all

# Coverage target: >1% global usage
> 1% and last 2 versions